title: U.S. Census, Annual estimates of birth rates by county Year 00 to 09, USA, March 27, 2010
name: U.S. Census, Annual estimates of birth rates by county Year 00 to 09, USA, March 27, 2010
description:
The U.S. Census released the annualized population estimates between Year 2000 and 2009 by county data on 25th March, 2010.  
The poly shapefile shows number of births rates by county from 2000 to 2009. 
Elsewhere on Finder! you may look for population data on deaths, births and death rates, migration, migration rates, international migration, international migration rates etc. 
Use keyword Census, Population, birth-rates, death-rates, migration-rates, international-migration etc.

Note: the attributes all start with letter R which stands for Rate thus
RBirth09 = birth rates in 2009
